top.value: 1. Ensure effective, sufficient and continuous provision of life saving water and sanitation services for targeted men, women, boys, and girls. 2. Ensure that all targeted men, women, boys and girls, have the means and are encouraged to adopt individual and collective measures of hygiene to mitigate individual and public health risks. 3. Ensure that all WASH assistance promotes the protections safety and dignity of targeted people and is used equitably by men, women, boys and girls
